preference.name: SE_Trace_Report_Layout
preference.preference_description: Controls the arrangement of the panes in the Traceability view. Valid Values: true - Panes are arranged horizontally, with the Defining Object pane on the left and the Complying Object pane on the right. false - Panes are arranged vertically, with the Defining Object pane on top and the Complying Object pane at bottom.
